  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Mathematical Chain showcase emphasizing Quantum Smear. ORACLE's GENDY stochastic synthesis produces tones that are already spectrally indeterminate. Quantum Smear at Observation 0.12 (heavily uncollapsed superposition) wraps these tones in a dense reverb where the delay time itself is uncertain — adding another layer of spectral indeterminacy on top of the engine's own. Entropy Cooler at Stability 0.55 provides a mild ordering force. Voronoi Shatter at Crystallize 0.3 adds geometric fragmentation to the sustained tones. Attractor Drive minimal — the engine provides enough distortion character already.",
